g.text: [In case the actor wishes to filter the catalog again]
[In case the actor wishes to select another presentation order again]
4.1: Asks the actor if he wishes to filter the catalog again
3.2: Asks the actor if he wishes to select another presentation order of the catalog
2.1: Shows all the presentation order options and asks to select one (eg.growing/descending brand name, growing/descending description...)
1.1: Presents all the possible filter options (brand,description,status,category...)
3: Selects the presentation order of the catalog
2: Filters the catalog choosing the desired filter option
1: Requests to see the products catalog
Visual Paradigm Standard(MiguelJordão(1201487(Instituto Superior de Engenharia do Porto))
